<TEXT>
<P>
The advertising firm Saatchi &amp; Saatchi has named Gregory J. Mazares vice 
president and director of marketing and corporate planning for its legal and 
scientific consulting division. Mazares will also oversee marketing and 
strategic planning for Litigation Sciences Inc., a jury research and trial 
consulting firm in Rolling Hills Estates and acquired by Saatchi &amp; Saatchi 
in 1987. 
</P>
