DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE (U.S.) -- CONTRACTS; WIRE FRAUD; CONSPIRACY; BRIBERY; 
CLASSIFIED INFORMATION; INSIDER INFORMATION; POLITICAL CORRUPTION; GOVERNMENT 
MISCONDUCT 
</P>
