<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA033089-0080 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 37414 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 30, 1989, Thursday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part 5; Page 22; Column 5 
</P>
