The West Los Angeles office of George Smith/Grubb &amp; Ellis Financial 
Services raised nearly $14,000 for the California Special Olympics in a 
bowl-a-thon at Bay Shore Bowl in Santa Monica, according to the firm. The 
summer games will be held June 23-25 at UCLA. 
