DOWNTOWN DRIVE WILL COST $5 IN ITALIAN CITY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
FLORENCE, Italy 
</P>
