Officials said Arikan was detained and will appear at a hearing today. 
</P>
<P>
Members of Parliament are allowed to carry guns. However, no one is allowed to 
enter Parliament armed, although one official said it is not always possible to 
search deputies for arms. 
</P>
<P>
