W. VIRGINIA VOTES TO IMPEACH TREASURER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
CHARLESTON, W. Va. 
</P>
