BUSINESS ETHICS; PICO KOREA LTD; PICO MACOM INC; RIOTS -- SOUTH KOREA; 
AMERICANS -- SOUTH KOREA; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN INVESTMENTS -- SOUTH KOREA; 
LIQUIDATION 
</P>
