INVESTMENTS -- JAPAN; OFFICE EQUIPMENT; CORPORATE RESTRUCTURING; TOSHIBA CORP; 
TOSHIBA AMERICA INFORMATION SYSTEMS; EMPLOYMENT -- ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
