GROUND PINK, RUSS ARASMITH / Los Angeles Times ; Drawing, SHOOTING STAR, RUSS 
ARASMITH / Los Angeles Times ; Drawing, CALIFORNIA POPPY, RUSS ARASMITH / Los 
Angeles Times ; Drawing, PURPLE NIGHTSHADE, RUSS ARASMITH / Los Angeles Times ; 
Drawing, LUPINE, RUSS ARASMITH / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
